text: Alexander Skinner may refer to: * Al Skinner (baseball) (1856–1901), Major League Baseball player * Alexander Skinner (surgeon) (1743–1788), surgeon in the Continental Army during the American Revolution * Alexander Skinner (politician) (1910–1968), member of the Queensland Legislative Assembly * Xander Skinner (born 1998), Namibian swimmer
title: Alexander Skinner
